        "description"            : "Single source of truth for all Noble Architecture standard edge linework colours. Used by Na__EdgeUtil__PaintDeepNestedEdges to create SketchUp edge materials and populate the colour palette UI. Each colour key becomes the SketchUp material name when applied to edges.",
