        "divergenceNote"         : "This naming format (00_XX__LineColour__) diverges from the MAT face-material convention (MAT{NNN}__). Edge materials are candidates for alignment to a unified prefix scheme (e.g. EMT{NNNN}__) in a future consolidation pass.",
